## Architecture Reminder

Your `temp.md` defines this layered flow вЂ” **not** flat MVC. Business logic goes in **Services**, not Controllers.

```
Router  в†’  registers endpoints (/api/v1/auth, /api/v1/departments, etc.)
   в”‚
Controller  в†’  receives HTTP request, validates, calls service, returns response
   в”‚
Service  в†’  business logic (validation rules, hashing, token generation, etc.)
   в”‚
Repository  в†’  database queries (SQLAlchemy async)
   в”‚
Database  в†’  PostgreSQL
```

